column5: Today I received two fishing magazines in the mail... not one, TWO!  One more reason why my wife thinks I'm a wack-job.
only 2 you have a long way to go to be called a wack-job
2 in 1 day is rare... I only subscribe to 3 fishing related mags.
Sometimes the smallest things in life give you the greatest pleasures.  I can relate.

My wifes Grandfather passed away a few years ago but her grandmother doesn't want to cancel his subscriptions, so he was a great man in life and I still get gifts from him each and every month! ;o) wish he was still around so we could hit the lake!
I received my new sonar/gps combo today and put it aside to read outdoor Canada lol

What do you guys subscribe to now a days? I've been considering re subscribing but I'm not sure what to choose. I used to have subs to in fisherman, ontario out of doors, outdoor canada, bob izumi's real fishing, canadian fly fishing and a american one. Based on the content what would you guys recommend? I stopped renewing when I realized I had 2 big boxes full of fishing mags a few years ago lol
I received 2 also on Monday: In-Fisherman (best mag ever) and OOD.
You are talking about fish mags right Mike  I dont subscribe. I just pic off the shelf what interests me.
